<%- include("partials/header",{relativePath: ""}) -%>
<!-- body -->
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <h1 class="center-text padding-top">Welcome to Plant-Based Triathlete</h1>
    <p class="welcomeParagraph">Feel free to browse my collection of recipes and blog to follow me thru my triathlete journey!</p>
  </div>
  <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-interval="3000" data-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active black-bg">
        <h2 class="text-white center-text padding-top">Follow My Blog to Get Race Updates and Recaps</h2>
        <img src="imgs/iron-man.jpg" class="site-info-image padding-bottom-2" alt="...">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item black-bg">
        <h2 class="text-white center-text padding-top">Recieve Up To Date Training Information and Join Me Trough My Triathlete Journey</h2>
        <img src="imgs/GMR.jpg" class="site-info-image padding-bottom-2" alt="...">
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item black-bg">
        <h2 class="text-white center-text padding-top">Browse Through My Plant-Based Recipes</h2>
        <img src="imgs/french-toast.jpg" class="site-info-image padding-bottom-2" alt="...">
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 center-text">
        <img src="imgs/aboutMeImage.jpg" alt="Cycling-Image">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 center-text">
      <h2 class="padding-top">A little about me:</h2>
      <p>I started my plant-based journey in 2016 after watching the documentary <em>Forks Over Knives</em>.
      After I got the hang of it, I loved my new life style, but something was missing. I heard an inner
    calling to do traithlon, but was super scared of riding bikes(yes, the bike!). I eventually got over that fear and had my
    first sprint triathlon in March 2019. I have been obsessed ever since! I have created this website to
    help share my experiences with you and give you amazing recipes for a plant based life style.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
